      },
      {
        "text": "### Choose your data\n- **Choose two numerical columns** you want to compare.\n-  **Filter out any blank cells** in those columns.",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/320d00cfdc333568de18ff4fd62707d5-work_in_progress.png",
        "key": "hardware-components-60bbd87e-b298-4721-8344-14ba7f84abc6",
        "layout": "text-bottom-right",
        "fadeInOverPrevious": true
      },
      {
        "text": "### Create your chart\n- **Highlight both columns** of values. (Use Command/Ctrl to select non-adjacent columns.)\n- Go to **Insert → Chart** and choose **Scatter chart** as the chart type.",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/320d00cfdc333568de18ff4fd62707d5-work_in_progress.png",
        "key": "emma-scatter-plot-panel-data-science-lesson7-_2025_launch-d8015b75-22a2-49f3-a063-be193119fab1",
        "fadeInOverPrevious": false
      },
      {
        "text": "### If needed, change axes\n-  If you need to, **switch the X and Y axes**, click the chart and adjust the settings under **X-axis** and **Series**.",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/320d00cfdc333568de18ff4fd62707d5-work_in_progress.png",
        "key": "emma-scatter-plot-panel-data-science-lesson7-_2025_launch-ca1375da-1974-4c82-be0a-5ae54aa3bdac",
        "fadeInOverPrevious": false
      },
      {
        "text": "### Add in a title and customize axes labels\n- Go to the **Customize** tab \n- Open the **Chart & axis titles** toggle and update these parts of your chart",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/320d00cfdc333568de18ff4fd62707d5-work_in_progress.png",
        "key": "emma-scatter-plot-panel-data-science-lesson7-_2025_launch-d3540300-0c30-4ab5-a3ff-b173eb7d56f4",
